SHORT ARCHITECTURE SUMMARY (FOR DIPLOMA)
- Frontend UI + routing: src/main.tsx, src/App.tsx
- Frontend auth/session: src/store/authStore.ts
- Frontend chess gameplay (bot + online): src/hooks/useStockfishGame.ts, src/hooks/useOnlineQuickMatch.ts, src/hooks/useFriendOnlineGame.ts
- Backend realtime/game server: server/index.js

These 7 files are the best "main code" set to explain the whole system clearly in a diploma report.

